data.description: 4 Bedroom home with A/C 2022, with Solar Panels 2019 and New Furnace 2022!  Home is in a Great location for quick access to Peterson A/F, Shriever A/F and Ft Carson, Amazon Distribution Center, C/S Airport and Fountain Blvd to I25.  Large xeriscape front and back yard.  Upon entering this lovely home you will like the open floor plan with the bay window in the living room showing the great views of the mountain range, the electric fireplace with the built in wood mantel offer a cozy atmosphere for a welcoming gathering place.  State of the Art Refrigerator is a nice feature.  Window above the deep sink looks out to the spacious back yard.  The laundry space is on the main level, a full bath and bedroom.  The upper level has 3 bedrooms.  The Master suite has an organized closet with direct door to the full bath.  The concrete patio is a great size for barbecues.  Privacy fenced in back yard with garden boxes and a storage shed.
